text.section:
Any lease proposed to be awarded under this section, including all lease renewals for which the annual rental cost will exceed one hundred thousand dollars ($100,000), shall be reported to the Capital Projects and Bond Oversight Committee after drafting of the lease is completed but before execution. The report shall include:
The name of the agency that will occupy the premises;
The name of the lessor;
The purpose and justification for the lease;
The terms of the lease;
An explanation of why the Finance and Administration Cabinet chose this lessor; and
A survey and cost comparison of similar rental properties within the area.
